  <summary date="2021-04-08T19:37:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Digital Commodity Exchange Act of 2020 

This bill provides for the regulation and registration of digital commodity exchanges. Digital commodity exchanges are subject to oversight by the Commodity Futures Trading Commission. The bill establishes the conditions for the sale of digital commodities, the registration of exchanges, and sets forth other requirements.</summary>
